articles.title: At least 25 dead in landslides, floods after tropical storm Megi hits Philippines - CNN
articles.description: Philippine authorities said on Monday at least 25 people had died in landslides and floods caused by tropical storm Megi as it hit the eastern and southern coasts of the Southeast Asian country.
